# Development Tools

## Script Categories
- build: Build and bundling scripts
- lint: Code linting and formatting tools
- test: Testing utilities and helpers
- generate: Code generation scripts
- deploy: Deployment automation

## Usage Guidelines
- All scripts should be executable from package.json
- Use TypeScript for complex scripts
- Document script purpose and parameters
- Handle errors gracefully with meaningful messages
- Use consistent naming conventions

## Tool Dependencies
- ESLint: Code linting
- Prettier: Code formatting
- Husky: Git hooks
- lint-staged: Run linters on staged files